# The shipped, pre-trained knowledge store is the TRACKED binary knowledge.sqlite
# (spec D14; a fresh clone must behave identically off committed knowledge, so it
# stays tracked — the 2026-06-23 "gitignore the binary" migration was reverted).
# Mark it binary so git never attempts a textual diff or line-ending conversion of
# the blob (cleaner `git log -p` / `git diff`; avoids CRLF corruption on any host).
# This does NOT auto-merge concurrent operator edits: the store is a local working
# copy and cross-operator experience-sharing goes through the additive, honesty-
# gated knowledge_sync.py NDJSON bundle (knowledge/store/), never a git binary merge.
# (Not using `merge=ours`: that driver needs an unshared `git config
# merge.ours.driver true`, so it silently no-ops on a fresh clone — codex-debug
# 2026-07-13 #5.)  heuristics.json is left as normal text so recipe deltas stay
# reviewable in a diff.
r2g-skills/signoff-loop/knowledge/knowledge.sqlite binary
